{"metadata":{"title":"Theming","modules":[{"name":"IronUI"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"IronUI’s theming system provides six categories of design tokens that control every aspect of your app’s visual appearance. Tokens automatically adapt between light and dark modes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Token Categories","anchor":"Token-Categories","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"text":"Color Tokens","anchor":"Color-Tokens","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"25 semantic colors organized by purpose:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["theme.colors.primary          \/\/ Brand primary color","theme.colors.secondary        \/\/ Supporting color","theme.colors.background       \/\/ Page background","theme.colors.surface          \/\/ Card\/component background","theme.colors.surfaceElevated  \/\/ Elevated surfaces","theme.colors.border           \/\/ Borders and dividers","theme.colors.textPrimary      \/\/ Primary text","theme.colors.textSecondary    \/\/ Secondary text","theme.colors.success          \/\/ Success states","theme.colors.warning          \/\/ Warning states","theme.colors.error            \/\/ Error states","theme.colors.info             \/\/ Informational states"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":3,"text":"Typography Tokens","anchor":"Typography-Tokens","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"15 font styles following a consistent scale:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["theme.typography.displayLarge   \/\/ Hero text (57pt)","theme.typography.displayMedium  \/\/ Large display (45pt)","theme.typography.headlineLarge  \/\/ Section headers (32pt)","theme.typography.titleLarge     \/\/ Card titles (22pt)","theme.typography.bodyLarge      \/\/ Primary content (17pt)","theme.typography.bodyMedium     \/\/ Default